headline.main: US Admiral in Disputed South China Sea: 'We Will Be Here'
headline.print_headline: US Admiral in Disputed South China Sea: 'We Will Be Here'

lead_paragraph: America will continue to patrol the South China Sea to ensure freedom of navigation and overflight in the disputed region, a U.S. admiral said Friday amid questions whether U.S. involvement in one of Asia's potential flashpoints will change.
